ld\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He plans to print the words on the murals in English and French so that the message is universally understood.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9876350192576024, \"rank\": 0.012101303680967603, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"the murals\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"English\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The murals will also include Chinese, Hebrew, Arabic and Russian symbols.To make this project successful, Holbrook received $150,000 from the Louis Wolfson Foundation and theMiami-basedPinnacle Housing Groupto get needed supplies and to work out logistics with the property owners of the four buildings.In the last 24 years, Holbrook says he has painted more than 400 murals in the Pittsburgh area and 150 in Miami, where he resides part of the time.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9963108875746797, \"rank\": 0.002530308014094906, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997795484463934, \"rank\": 0.00011484840460204247, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1935, \"end\": 1943, \"title